OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny intervals. There
OL,7,Fwill be a scattering of showers, these
OL,8,Fmainly in the north. Showers dying out
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first this evening.
OL,12,FOtherwise a cloudy night with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast.
OL,14,FRain turning more persistent across
OL,15,FGalloway later. Freshening southerly
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,19,Ftime in the morning. Then turning
OL,20,Fbrighter with a few showers. Brisk
OL,21,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
